### Create event (teacher/admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

{
  "title": "Workshop",
  "summary": "A short workshop",
  "startsAt": "2026-01-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "endsAt": "2026-01-01T12:00:00.000Z"
}

### Update event (owner or admin)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/events/{{event_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

{
  "title": "Updated title"
}

### Create registration (student)
POST http://localhost:3000/events/{{event_id}}/registrations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

{
  "note": "Looking forward"
}
